Iberdrola Scottish Unit to Invest $5 Billion Over 10 Years in Scotland

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-08-18T06:23:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/iberdrola-to-invest-3-billion-pounds-over-ten-years-in-scotland.html
Iberdrola SA (IBE) ’s ScottishPower unit
will invest 3 billion pounds ($4.96 billion) in Scotland’s power
distribution network over the next decade, ScottishPower said in
a statement on its  website.   To contact the reporter on this story:
